my wisdom with you.

05:59.092 --> 06:01.061
Janice, how's it going in there?

06:01.094 --> 06:02.596
- You tell me.

06:02.630 --> 06:04.998
What do you think?
- Oh, my God.

06:05.032 --> 06:06.600
Beyond love.

06:06.634 --> 06:08.436
Jill, this is
my bridesmaids' dress.

06:08.436 --> 06:09.437
Isn't it heaven?

06:09.437 --> 06:10.438
- Yeah.

06:10.438 --> 06:11.439
I mean, it might be

06:11.439 --> 06:13.607
