Oh, no, no, no, no.

06:15.976 --> 06:17.044
This is for the other girls.

06:17.077 --> 06:18.612
They're by Amsale.

06:18.646 --> 06:21.482
I have something much more
age-appropriate for you.

06:21.515 --> 06:23.451
Janice here definitely
has the booty for it.

06:23.451 --> 06:25.453
- Seriously,
it runs in my family.

06:25.453 --> 06:26.920
- Yeah.

06:26.954 --> 06:27.921
- Well, that was easy.

06:27.955 --> 06:29.657
- Yeah.

06:29.690 --> 06:32.593
Isn't that color the best
for her skin tone?

06:32.626 --> 06:35.663
She's so Lupita Nyong'o.

06:35.696 --> 06:37.130
- I don't see that.

06:37.164 --> 06:39.633
- Tara, the gown.

06:39.667 --> 06:43.571
Here is your
matron of honor gown.

06:43.604 --> 06:44.705
Bring it in.

06:44.738 --> 06:45.839
Thank you.

06:47.174 --> 06:48.476
- Holy shit.

06:48.476 --> 06:49.477
- I know.

06:49.510 --> 06:51.111
Gorgeous, right?

06:51.144 --> 06:54.047
I thought if anyone
can pull off a drapey sheath,

06:54.081 --> 06:55.649
it's J-to-the-izzle.

06:55.683 --> 06:58.486
- Is this also Amsale?

06:59.853 --> 07:01.388
- Sweetie, no.

07:01.489 --> 07:02.756
It's someone else.

07:02.790 --> 07:05.493
And listen, about your career.

07:05.493 --> 07:06.994
It may not feel this way,

07:07.027 --> 07:08.629
but I'm doing you a favor

07:08.662 --> 07:10.030
by not handing you a job.

07:10.063 --> 07:12.132
You'll get there
on your own, like I did,

07:12.165 --> 07:15.402
