to be connected

08:02.850 --> 08:04.652
to your Alzheimer's department?

08:04.685 --> 08:06.153
Why did I
divorce Graham again?

08:06.186 --> 08:07.988
- Is this a trick question?
I give up.

08:08.021 --> 08:09.557
- I seriously can't remember,

08:09.557 --> 08:10.724
and he's taking me out
to dinner,

08:10.758 --> 08:12.059
and I need to be armed.

08:12.092 --> 08:13.594
