he was always rude to your mom--

08:20.133 --> 08:21.969
- Well, she doesn't
understand sarcasm.

08:22.002 --> 08:23.070
- Also, he's a know-it-all.

08:23.103 --> 08:24.572
- Yeah, but to be fair,

08:24.572 --> 08:25.739
I should read international news

08:25.773 --> 08:27.040
