Come on up.

08:41.689 --> 08:42.956
And speaking of sucking,

08:42.990 --> 08:44.925
I asked Brooke
for a photo assignment,

08:44.958 --> 08:46.193
and she told me

08:46.226 --> 08:48.128
she doesn't mix
work with family.

08:48.161 --> 08:49.963
- Oh, you should know by now
not to listen to me.

08:49.997 --> 08:50.964
- It's okay.

08:50.998 --> 08:52.700
Humiliation is my jet fuel.

08:52.733 --> 08:54.067
