08:58.606 --> 08:59.773
- Okay, Carlton.

08:59.807 --> 09:01.108
Give me a deep breath.

09:01.141 --> 09:02.109
[exhales loudly]

09:02.142 --> 09:03.110
- [exhales]

09:03.143 --> 09:04.612
- Okay, perfect.
Now--

09:04.645 --> 09:06.780
[sings a scale]

09:06.814 --> 09:09.016
- [sings a scale]

09:09.049 --> 09:10.784
- Now a big laugh.
[laughs]

09:10.818 --> 09:11.785
- [laughing]

09:11.819 --> 09:13.120
- Ah, there we go.

09:13.153 --> 09:14.655
This is great.

09:14.688 --> 09:16.757
There's the smile
I was looking for.

09:16.790 --> 09:18.759
There's a bubbly personality
under that uniform.

09:18.792 --> 09:19.793
[camera shutter clicks]

09:19.827 --> 09:21.094
This is great.

09:21.128 --> 09:23.764
Okay, I think we have plenty
for the union.

09:23.797 --> 09:25.666
- Aw, I was just
starting to have fun.

09:25.699 --> 09:26.934
- Really?

09:26.967 --> 09:28.802
I mean, if you have
a little extra time,

09:28.836 --> 09:30.638
I'm trying to build up
my portfolio.

09:30.638 --> 09:32.640
We could do a few more
that are, like, looser,

09:32.640 --> 09:34.007
a little more "arty."

09:34.041 --> 09:35.242
- Um...

09:35.275 --> 09:36.744
[laughs]

09:36.777 --> 09:37.778
- No, if not, no worries.

09:37.811 --> 09:40.247
- Um...okay, sure.

09:40.280 --> 09:41.248
Why not?

09:41.281 --> 09:42.249
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

09:42.282 --> 09:43.250
- Okay, great.

09:43.283 --> 09:44.685
Let me just go get another lens.

09:44.718 --> 09:45.686
I'll be right back.

09:45.719 --> 09:46.687
Stand by.

09:46.720 --> 09:48.321
- [chuckles]

09:48.355 --> 09:50.891
- It'll just be a second.

09:50.924 --> 09:52.960
Normally I like to use
a medium lens

09:52.993 --> 09:54.027
for a portrait.

09:54.061 --> 09:55.562
Here we go.

09:55.663 --> 09:57.330
*

09:57.364 --> 09:58.699
This one will get me closer,

09:58.732 --> 10:01.134
so we can capture
every single...

10:01.168 --> 10:03.871
